<dspace:layout locbar="off" title="Why should you use Earth-prints?">
   <table width="95%" align="center">
        <tr>
            <td><h1>Why should you use Earth-prints?</h1>

    <ul>
    <li>To ensure global availability and preservation of your work</li>
    <li>To create a full text archive of your work that can be linked from your personal web pages</li>
    <li>To make your research available even before publication (many publishers allow this)</li>
    <li>To make unpublished material available</li>
    <li>To participate in the Open Access movement, removing cost and permission barriers for users of scholarly research</li>
    </ul></td>
        </tr>
